|                         |                              | balance quality.                   |
+-------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| Cost of getting wrong   | Unplanned outage:            | Planned outage at optimal time:    |
|                         | $500K-$2M/day.               | ~$50K. 10-40x savings.            |
+-------------------------+------------------------------+------------------------------------+

```

